ass="attachment-medium size-medium" alt="Cimarosa 2" srcset="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Cimarosa-2-136x200.jpg 136w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Cimarosa-2-522x768.jpg 522w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Cimarosa-2-270x396.jpg 270w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Cimarosa-2.jpg 653w" sizes="(max-width: 136px) 100vw, 136px" /></li><li class="gallery-item"><img width="133" height="200" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Cimarosa-1-133x200.jpg" class="attachment-medium size-medium" alt="Cimarosa 1" srcset="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Cimarosa-1-133x200.jpg 133w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Cimarosa-1-511x768.jpg 511w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Cimarosa-1-270x405.jpg 270w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Cimarosa-1.jpg 639w" sizes="(max-width: 133px) 100vw, 133px" /></li><li class="gallery-item"><img width="290" height="197" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Cimarosa-13-290x197.jpg" class="attachment-medium size-medium" alt="Cimarosa 13" srcset="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Cimarosa-13-290x197.jpg 290w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Cimarosa-13-270x183.jpg 270w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Cimarosa-13.jpg 960w" sizes="(max-width: 290px) 100vw, 290px" /></li></ul></div></div></p><p></em></p> <a class="wpptopdf" target="_blank" rel="noindex,nofollow" href="http://www.gbopera.it/2011/12/cimarosa-in-un-grazio-villaggio-vacanze/?format=pdf" title="Download PDF"><img alt="Download PDF" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/plugins/wp-post-to-pdf/asset/images/pdf.png"></a></div><div class="clear"></div><div class="entry-extra clearfix"><div class="comments-link " style="color: #363636"> <i class="icon-comment"></i> <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2011/12/cimarosa-in-un-grazio-villaggio-vacanze/#comments">1 Reply</a></div>